  "keyFeatures": [
    "Normalized price data across 39 CS2 marketplaces including BUFF163, CSFloat, Skinport, Steam, and more",
    "Real-time lowest asks and highest buy orders served from a Redis-first index with 5–10 minute freshness",
    "Doppler phase differentiation for items like Sapphire, Ruby, and Black Pearl variants",
    "OHLCV candle history up to 365 days with 5m, 1h, and 1d intervals",
    "Cross-market arbitrage scanner ranking opportunities by estimated net profit after fees",
    "Technical indicators (RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, ATR, VWAP, OBV) from composite candle data",
    "Portfolio management with Steam inventory import, CSV import/export, and transaction ledger",
    "Webhook delivery for price and spread alerts with signing secret verification",
    "Child API keys (sub-keys) for Quant accounts to sub-lease access with quota and rate overrides",
    "160+ ISO 4217 currency support with live FX conversion"
  ],
